{"tid":1669014,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台陸委會去信港府　提出派員到港押送陳同佳　要求港府提供認罪書口供","createTime":"2019-10-22T10:06:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T10:37:56.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a6456d31787a8e9b7065f0ca53a6f08ccd268730","tid":1669014,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T10:06:31.000Z","msg":"台灣殺人疑犯陳同佳明日刑滿出獄，陳同佳早前去信特首林鄭月娥，表示願意到台灣自首，但台灣政府對相關安排仍未有共識。台灣陸委會下午去信港府，提出台灣派員到香港，將陳同佳押回台灣受審，同時要求港府提供陳同佳的認罪書、口供以及確認身份。<br />\n<br />\n稍後有更詳細報道。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%8F%B0%E9%99%B8%E5%A7%94%E6%9C%83%E5%8E%BB%E4%BF%A1%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9C-%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E6%B4%BE%E5%93%A1%E5%88%B0%E6%B8%AF%E6%8A%BC%E9%80%81%E9%99%B3%E5%90%8C%E4%BD%B3-%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9C%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E8%AA%8D%E7%BD%AA%E6%9B%B8%E5%8F%A3%E4%BE%9B/?fbclid=IwAR0sOQlCqcMWosPPbBQfuO5yVee1Xji8Z8951P4H0wtPro-BFWd7a6sm4NU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%258F%25B0%25E9%2599%25B8%25E5%25A7%2594%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%258E%25BB%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25BA%259C-%25E6%258F%2590%25E5%2587%25BA%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%2588%25B0%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%258A%25BC%25E9%2580%2581%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%2590%258C%25E4%25BD%25B3-%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E6%258F%2590%25E4%25BE%259B%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%259B%25B8%25E5%258F%25A3%25E4%25BE%259B%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0sOQlCqcMWosPPbBQfuO5yVee1Xji8Z8951P4H0wtPro-BFWd7a6sm4NU&d=tlSH0trWbW1MAbtCTa3DUxmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=78f30a81\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%258F%25B0%25E9%2599%25B8%25E5%25A7%2594%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%258E%25BB%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25BA%259C-%25E6%258F%2590%25E5%2587%25BA%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%2588%25B0%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%258A%25BC%25E9%2580%2581%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%2590%258C%25E4%25BD%25B3-%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25